
{{#if user.isStudent}}
  <div>
    <h1>Welcome, {{user.displayName}}!</h1>
  </div>

{{else}}
 <div id="welcome" class="al_wtf home">
    <h1>Welcome to the EnCoMPASS Project</h1>
    <p> Here are some things you can do with EnCoMPASS: </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Craft responses to specific parts of your student's submission using noticing and wondering</li>
      <li>Invite peers to mark up and comment on your students' submissions</li>
      <li>Create a rubric from your filing of submissions</li>
      <li>Browse annotated submissions for a given problem to help inform your teaching</li>
      <li>Visualize your class' performance for a problem</li>
    </ul>

  {{#if user.isAuthenticated}}
    <p>	You'll probably want to get started by visiting your <span class="al_link">{{#link-to 'workspaces.index'}}workspaces{{/link-to}}</span>.</p>

    <p>Eventually we'd like to provide:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Visualize student or class work over time</li>
      <li>Visualize your mentoring over time</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      We'd love to hear your
      <a href="http://mathforum.org/cgi-bin/mailto.pl?key=92&to=the%20EnCoMPASS%20team">comments</a>.
    </p>
    <p><span class="al_link">{{#link-to 'problems'}}Create a Problem{{/link-to}}</span>.</p>
  {{else}}
    <h2>It looks like you are not logged in</h2>
    <p>Please login <a href="#/auth/login">here</a></p>
    <p>New to EnCoMPASS, sign up <a href="#/auth/signup">here</a></p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

{{/if}}
